by_statement: Rājakumāra Śarmā, Manīshā Tivārī, Mukeśa Kumāra Śarmā.

description.value: On the arts, literature, society, economy, culture, religion, administration, politics, and other topics of Rajasthan, India; data presented in tabular format.
